    <section class="ftco-section" id="role-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center mb-5 pb-5">
          <div class="col-md-7 heading-section text-center ftco-animate fadeInUp ftco-animated">
            <h1 class="big big-2">Role &amp; Responsibility</h1>
            <h2 class="mb-4">Role &amp; Responsibility</h2>
            <p>+ Identification of various channels for sourcing and recruitment.<br>
+ Shortlist the data from different Job Portal like–Indeed, Shine.com, Monster.com, Naukri.com <br>
+ Maintain the resources database of the organization.<br>
+ Recruiter the candidates according to the Job profile of Client.<br>
+ Preparing the Recruitment calendar with all the position and their target date of hire.<br>
+ Providing training and screening the profile according to the requirement of companies.<br>
+ Managing End to End recruitment through Jobsites, Walk-ins, referrals, advertisement,out-station hiring, headhunting for senior profiles.<br>
+ Organizing Drive and manage complete co-ordination with H.R and senior authority of the company.<br>
+ Focused on completing Targets on time and hiring as per budgeted headcount to ensure maximum revenue to the business<br>
+ Providing complete training regarding hiring to the recruiter and operated team of 6 employees.<br>
+ Managing Campus and Vendor drive.<br>
+ Recruit for IT, BPO, KPO, Banking, Engineering, Marketing and
Various sectors. <br>
+ Recruit profile for Lateral or senior hiring.<br>
</p>
